268
00:24:14,940 --> 00:24:16,700
After Qixuan and I betrayed our former sect,

269
00:24:16,700 --> 00:24:20,300
we escaped to that bamboo forest and found that shack.

270
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:23,600
We found this in the shack.

271
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:26,000
Back then, I was seriously wounded.

272
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:29,300
I only managed to survive thanks to your medicine.

273
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:33,400
And, I also received the help of Miss Yan Lingxia.

274
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:39,000
