275
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:41,500
And?

276
00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:45,200
And, you're strong enough.

277
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:52,740
Only those who are truly strong can lead us out of these icy plains.

278
00:24:52,740 --> 00:24:57,600
We only believe in the power of one's sword.

279
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:17,380
You two wanted to return to the sect, right?

280
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:19,360
Why are you two still here?

281
00:25:23,420 --> 00:25:25,500
Thank you, Sect Leader.

282
00:25:29,020 --> 00:25:30,780
