283
00:25:30,780 --> 00:25:34,080
 If one isn't strong enough, you'll end up as a pawn.

284
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:38,740
 That's why my father was accused of treason, and his entire clan was executed.

285
00:25:38,740 --> 00:25:41,100
